games.description:
Art Master Puzzle: Coloring Book is a new coloring game where you need to restore a picture from parts!

Start assembling the picture - initially the picture will be black and white. Look carefully at the pieces of the picture that will be displayed at the bottom of the screen and match them with the parts of the picture. Make a picture in full color and liven it up!

- Unique pictures to color and collect;
- An excellent combination of two genres - puzzles and coloring books;
- Bright and colorful color game graphics
- Free hints

